com.dhemery.publishing
Interface Distributor

All Known Subinterfaces:
Channel
All Known Implementing Classes:
MethodSubscriptionChannel
public interface Distributor

Distributes publications to subscribers. The nature of the publications and the nature of the delivery mechanism are left to implementors.
